---
---

<section id="privacy" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-12">
      Fast. Private. <span class="text-accent">Yours.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-bg-card">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Everything stays on your Mac</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">No cloud. No account. No tracking. Your clipboard history never leaves your machine.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-bg-card">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">SQLite + FTS5 in milliseconds</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Backed by SQLite with full-text search. Finds anything in your history before you finish typing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-bg-card">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Password managers ignored</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">1Password concealed items, transient clipboard entries, and auto-generated passwords are never stored.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-bg-card">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-accent">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Auto-cleanup</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Configurable retention by age and count. Drobu keeps what matters and cleans up the rest.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
